From a [comment|http://confluence.atlassian.com/display/BAMBOO/1.9+Specifying+Labels+for+a+Plan%27s+Build+Results?focusedCommentId=96076631#comment-96076631] in the Bamboo documentation:

{quote}The product UI and documentation are confusing on this point. Or perhaps it's just my belief that one should be able to have *multiple* regex->label rules for a plan. It doesn't ever say you can't but then, it doesn't say you can. And the product doesn't allow such.

Why do I think it should? Much like notifications, there's multiple distinct "events" that can occur in a build that should be labeled distinctly.{quote}

